  <brief_title>Study of the Use of Niaspan for Treatment of Dyslipidemia in Diabetic Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Trial of Niaspan® in Patients With Overt Diabetic Nephropathy and Moderate Renal Impairment</official_title>
